longBusinessSummary: Pangolin Diamonds Corp., together with its subsidiaries, engages in the acquisition, exploration, and development of mineral properties in Botswana. It holds 100% interest in eight diamond properties that include Tsabong North, Jwaneng South, Lorolwane, Mmadinare, Malatswae, Rehoboth, Machaneng South, and Motloutse River properties covering an area of approximately 10,705 square kilometers in Botswana. It also holds interest in Malatswae Diamond Property. The company was incorporated in 2011 and is headquartered in Toronto, Canada.
